cu.explanation_en: Setting SCTP_OUTSTREAMS to 999 exceeds the maximum allowed value, causing SCTP connection failure and preventing proper F1 interface setup.

du.explanation_en: Setting zeroCorrelationZoneConfig to 999 exceeds the maximum allowed value, causing configuration validation failure and preventing proper PRACH setup.
du.explanation_zh: 將 zeroCorrelationZoneConfig 設定為 999 超過最大允許值，會導致配置驗證失敗，並阻止正確的 PRACH 設置。
